{"tid":403493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】愛港力成員舉「這裡就是中國」標語　坐中大民主牆前與中大生對峙","createTime":"2017-09-17T08:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T09:06:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a109cefb455cf992a5081497dd280ce9e519be8","tid":403493,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170917/s00001/9600867add8d15bb3d4d55e3fb5cd87d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F9600867add8d15bb3d4d55e3fb5cd87d.jpg&h=86fe9756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文大學校長沈祖堯日前公開要求學生會盡快移除與「港獨」有關的宣傳品，否則校方會主動移除。今日下午約1時，記者在中大目擊先後有3名人士撕下文化廣場民主牆上印有「拒絕沉淪，唯有獨立」單張，其中一名白衣女子撕走民主牆上的標語時，正在當值的學生會外務秘書李文耀上前阻止並詢問身分，該女士未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n至下午約3時，「愛護香港力量」10多名成員中大文化廣場，高舉印有「這裏就是中國」等標語，並與學生對峙。10多人坐在民主牆前，並將橫額貼在民主牆上。10多名保安在場駐守。愛港力成員以「門口狗」稱呼早前與內地生互罵的中大學生會前會長周竪峰，又一度與在場持相反意見人士互相指罵。<br />\n<br />\n有成員強行將「這裡就是中國」的標語貼上民主牆，保安上前阻止期間，成員與其推阻，有女保安員一度跌倒地上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170917/s00001/1505636439195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F1505636439195&d=9ulIGd%2B19GD%2FoCX6EKh8F2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=0554a1d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F1505636439195&h=e5a5d85d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170917/s00001/1505636439195</a>"},{"pid":"f95510bd42c7d5817befe334db8984849881f1a5","tid":403493,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170917/s00001/9520d3cca42c87ae819b7edabf7c9efe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170917%2Fs00